Gnome VFS 0.3
-------------

Miscalaneous bug fixes.

Removed old metadata support.

Search method.

Gnome VFS 0.2
-------------

New in this release:

New MIME-type API.

MIME-type capplet now part of GnomeVFS.

Copy engine (gnome-vfs-xfer) now mostly implemented to support a file manager.

Symbolic link handling for simple links now working.

New FTP module.

WebDAV support.

Numerous fixes in the pthread backend.

Numerous memory and file descriptor leak fixes.

Numerous bug fixes.

Gnome VFS now builds without warnings.